    tmp = (wp.sin(0.58) + 0.32)
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.71) / 0.44) + ((v1 + 0.98 - v2 + 0.58) / (tmp + 0.11 + v2 + 0.28)))
    v2 = wp.exp(0.14)
    v2 = v0
